      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四蓝文堂、四大铠、余达、余兆、余光、余先、余德同上，同站门。〖牌子〗。旗夫、余化龙同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "余化龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某，余化龙。前者用瘟药将姜子牙人马迷倒，数日不见动静，适才探马报道，"
        },
        {
          "character": "余化龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姜尚复又兴兵前来，岂肯容他猖狂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余化龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众儿郎！城楼去者！"
        },
        {
          "character": "余化龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。余化龙上城。姜子牙、杨戬、韦陀、杨任、龙须虎、金吒、木吒、哪吒、雷震子、四文堂、四"
        },
        {
          "character": "余化龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大铠、四上手同上，同斜一字。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨戬、韦陀、杨任、龙须虎、金吒、木吒、哪吒、雷震子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是临潼关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜子牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "安营下寨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨戬、韦陀、杨任、龙须虎、金吒、木吒、哪吒、雷震子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "安营下寨。哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姜子牙、杨戬、韦陀、杨任、龙须虎、金吒、木吒、哪吒、雷震子、四文堂、四大铠、四上手同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "余化龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，儿啊，看姜尚人马犹如潮水一般，如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "余达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，爹爹，想是他国出了能人，解开瘟药也是有的。你我父子领兵出城与他决"
        },
        {
          "character": "余达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一死战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余化龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "余化龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，开城迎敌者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余化龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四蓝文堂、四大铠、余达、余兆、余光、余先、余德、余化龙同出城。姜子牙、杨戬、韦陀、杨任、龙须"
        },
        {
          "character": "余化龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虎、金吒、木吒、哪吒、雷震子、四文堂、四大铠、四上手同上，会阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "余化龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！马前来的敢是姜尚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜子牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！胆大余化龙，前者暗用瘟药将我军迷倒，今日整齐兵将与你分个胜负。"
        },
